\c 140
\s Umkhuleko wokucela ukulondolozwa
\d Kumqondisi wokuhlabelela. Isihlabelelo sikaDavida
\p
\v 1 Ngikhulula, N\nd kosi\x + Hlab. 119.153.\x*\nd*, emuntwini omubi\x + 140.4. Hlab. 71.4.\x*, ungilondoloze emuntwini olesihluku\x + 140.4. Hlab. 71.4.\x*,
\v 2 abaceba izinto ezimbi enhliziyweni, usuku lonke babuthanela izimpi\x + Hlab. 56.6.\x*.
\v 3 Balola ulimi lwabo\x + Hlab. 52.2. 140.11.\x* njengenyoka\x + Hlab. 58.4. Jobe 20.16.\x*, ubuhlungu\x + Hlab. 58.4. Jobe 20.16.\x* bebululu\x + Roma 3.13.\x* bungaphansi kwendebe zabo. \w Sela\w**\x + Hlab. 10.7.\x*.
\v 4 Ngilondoloze, N\nd kosi\nd*, ezandleni zomubi, ungivikele emuntwini olesihluku\x + 140.4. Hlab. 71.4.\x*; abaceba ukuwisa inyawo zami\x + Hlab. 36.12. 118.13.\x*.
\v 5 Abazigqajayo bangifihlele\x + Hlab. 35.7. 142.3. Jer. 18.22.\x* umjibila\x + Hlab. 142.3. Hlab. 91.3.\x*, lezintambo\x + Jobe 18.10.\x*, bendlala imbule eceleni kwendlela\x + Hlab. 9.15.\x*; bangibekela izithiyo. \w Sela\w**\x + Hlab. 64.5. Hlab. 141.9.\x*.
