\v 6 Ngithe eN\nd kosi\nd*ni: Wena unguNkulunkulu wami\x + Hlab. 142.5.\x*. Beka indlebe elizwini lokuncenga kwami, N\nd kosi\x + Hlab. 28.2,6. 31.22. 130.2. Hlab. 116.1. 143.1.\x*\nd*.
\v 7 Jehova, Nkosi, mandla osindiso lwami\x + Hlab. 28.8.\x*, wembese ikhanda lami\x + Hlab. 60.7.\x* osukwini lwezikhali\x + Jobe 39.21. Hez. 39.9,10.\x*.
\v 8 Unganiki, N\nd kosi\nd*, izifiso zomubi, ungaphumelelisi icebo lakhe elibi\x + Hlab. 35.25.\x*, \add hlezi\add* baziphakamise. \w Sela\w**\x + Dute. 32.27.\x*.
