\v 9 \add Nge\add*khanda labangihanqileyo, ububi bendebe zabo kabubembese\x + Zaga 18.7.\x*.
\v 10 Kakuthi amalahle atshisayo akhithikele phezu kwabo, ubawisela emlilweni, emigodini etshonayo, ukuze bangavuki\x + Hlab. 55.3.\x*.
\v 11 Umuntu wolimi kangamiswa elizweni; umuntu olesihluku, ububi buzamzingela kube yikuwiswa \add kwakhe\add*.
