\v 12 Ngiyazi ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* izasebenza udaba lohluphekayo\x + Hlab. 9.4.\x*, ilungelo labayanga\x + Hlab. 9.4.\x*\x + 1 Kho. 8.45,49,59.\x*.
\v 13 Isibili abalungileyo bazalidumisa ibizo lakho; abaqotho bazahlala ebusweni bakho\x + Hlab. 64.10.\x*.